  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Affiliate Marketing Specialist (Fashion E-commerce)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is Fashion brand established in Singapore. Due to their current expansion plan, they are looking for an Affiliate Marketing Specialist, in hopes of developing the current high performing Marketing team. They are located in the Central area – easily accessible.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Duties of Affiliate Marketing Specialist:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Platform Operations:</strong> Manage daily Impact platform tasks, including commissions, creatives, messaging, and contracts.</li><li><strong>Partner Recruitment:</strong> Source and onboard top-tier affiliates in Western markets, including bloggers, KOLs, and cashback sites.</li><li><strong>Campaigns:</strong> Plan and execute affiliate marketing programs for peak wedding seasons and promotions.</li><li><strong>Relationship Management:</strong> Maintain affiliate engagement and ensure consistent brand messaging.</li><li><strong>Data Analysis:</strong> Monitor GMV, traffic, and ROI; assess partner performance and optimise strategies.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree holder in Marketing, Business or relevant discipline</li><li>Min 3 - 5 years of experience in handling overseas affiliate marketing, with good understanding of e-commerce landscape for <strong>Fashion Retail </strong>industry</li><li>Familiar with Western market is highly preferable</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified</p><p><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.<br />EA License No. 19C9682<br />EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</p>",
